# Intentionally empty.
#
# This Unity project has NO project-local test code. All EditMode + PlayMode
# tests live INSIDE the org.unitedav package (unity/Tests/) and are discovered
# via the "testables": ["org.unitedav"] entry in Packages/manifest.json.
#
# Unity will create .meta files alongside the contents of this folder on first
# open; those are machine-generated and intentionally git-ignored for this
# throwaway harness (see ../.gitignore).
